{"tid":2240514,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"The Walking Dead 行屍 第十季劇情討論區 [2]","createTime":"2020-10-12T16:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T19:10:27.000Z","uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1c82336c9048c2d76ac52ac52a7073e44bb7b2d3","tid":2240514,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"本POST定位︰<br />\n只接受討論已經播映劇集及相關原著內容<br />\n請勿在此發放網絡上的劇透及原著未做到之劇情<br />\n粉紅細字亦不接受<br />\n<br />\n通常星期一中午前就會有SEED同晏少少就有埋英文字幕<br />\n鄰國SEED呀, 轉檔, 中字, 恕未能提供. 要睇美劇, 請到外國網搵:<br />\nSEED: (如當日上唔到請自行GOOGLE各大BT網, keyword The Walking Dead S08EXX, X=集數)<br />\n<a href=\"https://rarbg.to/torrents.php?search=the+walking+dead\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frarbg.to%2Ftorrents.php%3Fsearch%3Dthe%2Bwalking%2Bdead&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2VwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=6d48cd50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rarbg.to/torrents.php?search=the+walking+dead</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://eztv.ag/search/the-walking-dead\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feztv.ag%2Fsearch%2Fthe-walking-dead&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2VwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=72417ce7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eztv.ag/search/the-walking-dead</a><br />\n<br />\n英文字幕(通常當日下晝一兩點就出):<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.addic7ed.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.addic7ed.com&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2VwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=45e73de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.addic7ed.com</a>"},{"pid":"949bcc273fe97ca6456000916409561691d70fca","tid":2240514,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"上一個post太舊沉左底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於睇左season end<br />\n<br />\n雖然武肺影響 但都唔洗咁hea啊<br />\n<br />\n明明之前拍到wisper一個超大部落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今集我屌夾埋20個人都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ndaryl 引屍 同 主城個時間線好似兩個空間咁<br />\n<br />\nbeta同佢班o靚係樓下想爆上樓  --&gt; daryl 引完屍番黎天都黑撚埋--&gt; beta同佢班o靚仍然仲係樓下梅下梅下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0a3b1a86324c19017ee1863fe81ba11b590b38","tid":2240514,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"carol引屍落山腳又係on9<br />\n<br />\n如果訓低咁簡單就可以照引哂班屍行落去<br />\n<br />\n好心就唔好劇情鋪排到一定要有人犧牲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0912e9ab79904c4beaf9fb63f6706dacdc745335","tid":2240514,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"神父死守果度又係on9<br />\n<br />\n明明前一個shot已經斧頭打爆門<br />\n<br />\n之後又突然間tenet咁還原番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬連下戲得唔得"},{"pid":"48ab2b5558007fa8bbb9288648c4e48ba4ab014e","tid":2240514,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"原來已經開播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還我Carl Glenn!!!!!"},{"pid":"f982c26e2566d434c6932fd136f9c51080d652fa","tid":2240514,"uid":273014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"越睇越悶，好似打機不斷升lv、然後有新boss咁，同喪屍打鬥嗰種驚險感已經冇左"},{"pid":"befb8a5cf782dcfba16cd83bb2246c8c0973e7e9","tid":2240514,"uid":56702,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T18:13:53.000Z","msg":"究竟同tara走散咗嗰條黑鬼會唔會再出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6c65d346cbbce34e4132f8aa4f16685322adc7","tid":2240514,"uid":45821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T18:37:22.000Z","msg":"第十一季唔係2021年先有咩  早成年開post做咩"},{"pid":"abe9d2042ff38e656005dc3620b3fab53aad9c74","tid":2240514,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T18:58:41.000Z","msg":"唔係見到呢個post都唔知原來出咗season finale<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as